Types

Class AbsUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • Types.AbsUser
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    User

    public abstract class AbsUser
extends java.lang.Object
    It is an abstract class that provides basic methods and properties to other classes. Contains methods for successfully working with the future object:
    • Save the user
    • Get user's item /ul>

      Saving a user is done by connecting to the database and saving the user.

      Getting the user's item is done by connecting to the database and searching for an id.

    Since:
    1.0
